events.body:
@sipa: I tested it a lot before making the pull request, yes.  It seems to work well in db5.1.25.  I don't have db4.x.

@gavinandresen: I think the logs are so you can do database recovery in the event of a crash.

It seems that in the event of a crash we usually manage to clean up the logs before exiting however :)

I'll update my patch so it's not a command line option.
